{"title":"Juuksehooldus","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"rhubarb-hair-mask-with-castor-oil-250-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11509\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/5-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11514\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/6-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty global awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11524\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/8-300x300.png\" alt=\"global green beauty awards 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11519\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/7-300x300.png\" alt=\"buduaar beauty award 2022\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927707627847,"sku":"","price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-250ml-9001472.png?v=1763665705"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-250ml-1","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 200ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354507583815,"sku":null,"price":14.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-200ml-244590.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml","title":"NAIF Easy Styling Hair Lotion for Baby \u0026 Kids 150ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA hair lotion to tame and take care of wild kids hair. Naïf's Easy Styling Hair Lotion makes combing easier and reduces tangles and frizz for all hair types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHair lotion with natural ingredients that doesn't make the hair greasy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoftens knots and tangles in the hair and reduces frizz in curls\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCan also be used with cradle cap\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eFor use on babies and children, for all hairtypes\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDoes not contain microplastics, mineral oils, SLES or silicones\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSpray on towel-dried hair from 30 cm away. Massage gently, comb through the hair and style. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Methylpropanediol, Caprylyl\/Capryl Glucoside, Glycerin, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Inulin, Betaine, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Polyglyceryl-6 Oleate, Sodium Surfactin, Parfum\/Fragrance (allergen-free), Lactic Acid, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBottle made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446066323783,"sku":null,"price":14.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-easy-styling-hair-lotion-for-baby-kids-150ml-404694.png?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml","title":"HOIA Hydrating Hair Mist 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePleasantly scented hydrating spray helps to keep hair healthy, strong and shiny. Spray contains locally sourced nettle extract and rice water to strengthen hair, plant-based keratin, deeply moisturizing hyaluronic acid and aloe, hair-softening seaweed extracts and plant hydrosols, nourishing oils and shine-enhancing essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake the bottle before use and spray an appropriate amount onto wet or dry hair. No need to rinse hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Salvia Officinalis Distillate water, *Achillea Millefolium Distillate water, Oryza Sativa Seed water, Chodrus Crispus extract, Sargassum Fluitans\/Natans extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Crambe Abyssinica Seed oil, *Nigella Sativa Seed oil, Saccharomyces Ferment, Lactobacillus Ferment, Hydronated Sodium Hyaluronate, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf juice, Sodium Levulinate, Urtica Dioica Plant extract, Pentylene Glycol, Sodium Anisate, *Lavandula Angustifolia oil, *Pelargonium Graveolens oil, Citric Acid. **Citral, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Citronellol. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic. **Natural components of essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324565688647,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml-963057.jpg?v=1739897245"},{"product_id":"madara-feed-repair-dry-rescue-hair-mask-180ml","title":"MÁDARA FEED Repair \u0026 Dry Rescue hair mask 180ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eDeeply nourish your hair with this exceptional oil blend and fungi-based restructure mask that also prevents fiber damage , preserves colour and softens the hair.  Strengthens the lipid matrix and improves protection against mechanical damage and heat appliance to ensure silky smooth high-shine hair for days.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif;\"\u003e​​​​\u003c\/span\u003eApply to clean, damp hair lengths and ends. Leave in for 5–10 minutes and rinse out thoroughly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Cantharellus cibarius (chanterelle) extract, Cetearyl Alcohol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Brassica Alcohol, PCA Glyceryl Oleate, Sodium PCA, Brassicyl Isoleucinate Esylate, Lactic Acid, Aroma, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Xylitylglucoside, Butylene Glycol, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Benzyl Alcohol, Anhydroxylitol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Benzoate, Xylitol, Hydrolyzed Keratin, Potassium Sorbate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Oenothera Biennis (Evening Primrose) Oil, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Tocopherol, Crambe Maritima (Sea Kale) Leaf Extract, Leuconostoc\/Radish Root Ferment Filtrate, Linalool, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Juniperus Virginiana Oil, Benzyl Salicylate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50917384552775,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-feed-repair-dry-rescue-hair-mask-180ml-298387.png?v=1740808672"},{"product_id":"magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-travel-size-100-ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract Travel Size 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335117537607,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-travel-size-100ml-344835.png?v=1743213039"},{"product_id":"magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-refill-100ml","title":"Magrada Moisturizing Hair Mask with Rhubarb Extract Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVoluminous, shiny, healthy – we have created a professional hair care collection for you to enjoy beautiful salon hair every day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe gold medal-winning (Pure Beauty Global Awards 2021 Winner) hair mask is designed for intensive nurturing and moisturising of dry and damaged hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe rhubarb hair mask with castor oil and macadamia oil pampers, revives, and smooths damaged hair. The vitality of the plants has a balancing and nurturing effect. The natural care improves the hair structure and reduces damage, adding a captivating shine to the hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe silky, creamy composition will give the hair a spring-like freshness and the juicy aroma of rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThanks to its anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties, \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003erhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e soothes a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMacadamia oil\u003c\/span\u003e is rich in fatty acids and potassium, which will make your hair stronger and easier to comb. Macadamia oil contains antioxidants which help the hair to recover from damaging environmental impacts.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCastor oil\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-microbial effect, which helps to reduce dandruff and other scalp issues deteriorating hair health. The vitamin E in the oil moisturises hair roots and gives the hair a healthy shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the mask on damp hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 5–15 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Macadamia Ternifolia (Macadamia) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Hydrolyzed Wheat Starch, Parfum, Butylene Glycol, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Triethanolamine, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,16%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51335181631815,"sku":null,"price":30.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-moisturizing-hair-mask-with-rhubarb-extract-refill-500ml-702844.png?v=1743213040"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-50ml","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Apply after shampooing to towel-dried hair. Leave on for 5-10 minutes, then comb and rinse. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua, Behenamidopropyl dimethylamine, Cetearyl alcohol, Lactic acid, Phenoxyethanol, Parfum, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Tocopheryl acetate, Sorbitol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Olea europaea fruit oil*, Opuntia ficus-indica seed oil, Glycerin, Myrtus communis extract, Panthenol, Hamamelis virginiana leaf extract*, Mel*, Propolis, Retinyl palmitate, Limonene, Linalool, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138364764487,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-200ml-244590.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"bee-it-reconstruction-hair-mask-50ml-copy","title":"BEE IT Reconstruction Hair Mask 1000ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eA concentrated repairing post shampoo mask which gratifies for its immediate effectiveness. Gives strength and elasticity, deeply hydrating and nourishing for a healthy, luminous and plumped up hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-fam